htiger Beitrag zur Medien- und Wissensgeschichte der Bundesrepublik.  aThe defining medium of the post-war era as a helper of democracy - Melanie Fritscher-Fehr takes a close look at networks between broadcasting and the science of history that have been obscure until now.  afunded by Cusanuswerk - Bischöfliche Studienförderung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aBildung. 4aDemokratie. 4aDeutsche Geschichte. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtskultur. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aMedien. 4aMediengeschichte. 4aNachkriegszeit. 4aRe-education. 4aRundfunk. 4aWestdeutschland. 4aWissensgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Germany.2bisacsh  aBroadcasting.  aCultural History.  aCulture of History.  aDemocracy.  aEducation.  aGerman History.  aHistory of Knowledge.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aMedia History.  aMedia.  aPost-war.  aRe-education.  aWest Germany.2 aCusanuswerk - Bischöfliche Studienförderungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2019z9783110606195oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839441046zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839441046423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839441046/original  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019